Computer Science
Senior Project 2012

~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~


Invoking the top-level Maven project will build all 4 submodules:



tendril-domain: Provides platform-agnostic Java classes for Tendril's domain objects. 
SimpleXML (JSON should work too) annotations included. Also contains ITendril interface for 
interacting with the Tendril API.

tendril-android-lib: An Android library that depends on tendril-domain. Includes TendrilTemplate 
implementation of the ITendril interface using the Spring Android Library

tendril-example: A simple Android App that demonstrates usage of most of the API calls.

tendril-cirrus: Another Android App that uses geolocation.